data.title: Cybill Episodes
data.meta_description: Cybill episodes - Read online for free. This document provides episode summaries for the first two seasons of the TV show Cybill. In season 1, Cybill dates strangers and deals with family issues while pursuing acting roles. Her daughter Maryann has dating troubles of her own. In season 2, Cybill searches for meaning in her life and deals with romantic relationships with Ira and other men, while Maryann continues meddling in Cybill's love life. The episodes cover the personal and professional lives of Cybill and her family and friends.
